  "detailed_description": "Another puzzle game with hexagon grid, but difficult! Player must fill the grid with different shapes. Each line and area must not contain same shape, just like classic Sudoku game!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414270/extras/583784c288c3294c192910db7d7e2812.poster.avif?t=1723203476\" width=484 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414270/extras/583784c288c3294c192910db7d7e2812.webm?t=1723203476\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414270/extras/583784c288c3294c192910db7d7e2812.mp4?t=1723203476\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Feature</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>30 unique levels on main branch. Each level is crafted carefully and only have one possible answer.<br></li><li>10 unique levels for each side branch. You have to think differently on every side branch.<br></li><li>4 different beautiful skins for you to choose from.<br></li><li>Design your own puzzle and share with people on workshop!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414270/extras/8d3e8814e4bf4c18ebf0e0803a1059ac.poster.avif?t=1723203476\" width=484 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414270/extras/8d3e8814e4bf4c18ebf0e0803a1059ac.webm?t=1723203476\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414270/extras/8d3e8814e4bf4c18ebf0e0803a1059ac.mp4?t=1723203476\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
